Squadron, part of the 16th Special Operations Wing based at
Hurlburt Field in North Carolina State.
</P>
<P>
The Pave-Low can carry at least 38 troops and is equipped with
special navigation gear, radar and other electronics to help it
slip behind enemy lines without detection. 
