insurance business has been a success.
</P>
<P>
Feng Xiaozeng, the CIRC's vice-chairman, said at the opening of
the Shanghai International Seminar on Insurance today that China's
insurance business increased 1,000-fold in the past two decades,
with a yearly increase of 37.6 percent.
</P>
