May last year have been jailed by the Dongcheng District People's
Court.
</P>
<P>
Wang Jinlai, who built the Yuquanying Furniture City, and Zhang
Jianguo, the manager of the complex, were found guilty of
neglecting fire-control work, and sentenced to four years and
three years in prison, respectively.
</P>
<P>
