<HEADLINE> Chinese Military Experts Refute COX Report (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The expert, a participant in negotiations concerning joint Sino-
U.S. satellite launches, said security officials from the U.S.
Department of Defense participated in all negotiations. They
supervised both Chinese and U.S. technicians, and normal contacts
between participants from the two sides were closely monitored.
