<TEXT>

<P>
SHENZHEN, June 3 (Xinhua)-- Sierra Leone President Ahmad Tejan
Kabbah wound up his two-day visit in the well-known reform pilot
city of Shenzhen and left for Wuhan in central China's Hubei
Province this afternoon.
</P>
