China's ambassador to DPRK Wan Yongxiang, were among those
greeting the delegation at the airport.
</P>
<P>
Li Peng, chairman of the NPC Standing Committee, will preside
over a welcoming ceremony for Kim Yong Nam this afternoon. They
will also hold talks following the welcoming ceremony.  
